Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
get_visible_nets(25.10)                                get_visible_nets(25.10)

Name
       get_visible_nets  -  Returns the names of the visible nets if some nets
       have been hidden in the design

Syntax
       get_visible_nets

       [-help]

       Returns the names of the visible nets if some nets have been hidden  in
       the design. If all nets are visible, this command has no effect.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description that includes type and default infor-
              mation for each get_visible_nets parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man get_visible_nets

Examples
              * The  following command returns the name of all visible nets in
                the designs:

                innovus 17> get_visible_nets

                ram1/subram02_lower/TESTACT_INST_PERIWD-
                SRAM001PAA512W27C3/tpo_a_9_

Related Information
              * set_visible_nets

